sentences.english: BE, baby yesterday is also individually see, definite is very exquisite.
sentences.chinese: 是，孩兒昨天也是親眼所見，確實是非常玄妙。

sentences.english: Great minds think alike, but fools seldom differ.
sentences.chinese: 英雄所見略同，傻瓜很少意見不合。

sentences.english: Who says great minds think alike?
He that would live in peace and ease, must not speak all the knows, nor judge all he sees.
sentences.chinese: 若想生活得平靜安穩，對於所見所聞就不要妄加評論。

sentences.english: They told them all that had happened.
sentences.chinese: 然後告訴他們，他們所見的事。

sentences.english: WYSIWYG editing of animation effects. Tested on Win7 and works as intended.
sentences.chinese: 所見即所得編輯的動畫效果。

sentences.english: FOX was just repeating the information from people who claimed to be eye-witnesses.
sentences.chinese: 但FOX一直在重申，這些信息是目擊者親眼所見。

sentences.english: The spitting here we are talking is totally different from what we see every day.
sentences.chinese: 這裏的吐口水跟我們日常所見的意義完全是兩回事。

sentences.english: He seeth what I cannot see.
sentences.chinese: 因爲祂看見我所見不到的情境。

sentences.english: In my dream, the nameless lake is more colorful and everlasting changing than what I really see.
sentences.chinese: 在夢中，未名要比親眼所見的，更加絢爛和多變。

sentences.english: As you can see, the number of possible asset allocations is practically unlimited.
sentences.chinese: 如你所見，資產可能的分配方法可以說是無窮多的。

sentences.english: He sees more and comprehends more of what he sees.
sentences.chinese: 他看到的越多，就對所見領會地越多。

sentences.english: This photo shows the platforms and train depot of the station.
sentences.chinese: 圖中所見是竹東車站的月臺與車庫。

sentences.english: The flower racks or drying racks shown below are threatening the life of pedestrians .
sentences.chinese: 以下圖中所見的花架及晾衣架對路人的生命構成威脅。

sentences.english: Just my two cents' worth based on forty years' wandering around observing with eyes and ears open.
sentences.chinese: 這只是在下基於四十多年所見所聞的一點愚見，呵呵。

sentences.english: Identifying what you see does not tell where you are.
sentences.chinese: 辨識出你所見之物，並不能告訴你所在位置。
